data.title: Patricia Ann Steiger

HNYN
Patricia Ann Steiger
1325 Hillside Dr
Bettendorf, Iowa 52722-3089. Recipient Robert F. Tyson award Iowa Community Action Association, 1992, Lyndon Baines Johnson Human Svc. award, 1994.
data.text:
Background

Steiger, Patricia Ann was born on May 26, 1933 in Davenport, Iowa, United States. Daughter of Edmunnd John and DeMarys Catherine (McDonnell) Burke.

Career

National advertising assistant, Davenport (Iowa) Newspaper, 1952-1958; advertising assistant, Petersen's, Davenport, 1960-1961; program director, Iowa East Control T.R.A.I.N., Davenport, 1967-1969; deputy director, Iowa East Control T.R.A.I.N., Davenport, 1969-1971; executive director, Iowa East Control T.R.A.I.N., Davenport, since 1971.
